    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Rot-echoes are small, writhing masses of animated decay — vestigial imprints of creatures consumed by the Rot, briefly given form and hunger. They leave trails of blackened earth wherever they pass and drain Hit Die from those they touch. Spawned from corrupted nexuses or powerful Rot-bound creatures, a rot-echo swarm is a sign that the Rot's influence in an area has grown critical. Each one dissolves into difficult terrain when destroyed.</p>",
